Now, you should be able to read through the beautiful working of Ritambara Pragnya which is very subtle. And then you'll start enjoying the little, little things it plays to make you very happy and to give you what some artist must have done it long time back, which his desire was to fulfill Now, this is also we should say, is the work of Shri Ganesha. He resides as Omkara in the Ritambara Pragnya. He resides on the electromagnetic forces as the vibrations in the matter, in every atom. He resides in every ripple of our emotions which gives us joy. And He resides as a beautiful decoration of the Kundalini because she has the red and the gold color just like my sari. So as the color of the Kundalini He resides. But at Sahasrara, He becomes the joy, at Mooladhara as the fragrance, and every memory of mind should give you fragrance because He is the Lord of memory.

So this is how He manages everything so beautifully. He's such an innocent person who plays around his beauty to make us happy. Our children should also make us very happy if we have brought them up properly. But if we have been all the time busy with lust and greed the children cannot be good children. They cannot represent Ganesh's tattva as it should be.

